Explanation:

We create a map for food items, cuisine, and food-cuisine combinations. When a rating is changed, we update the cuisineFoodMap to store the updated food-cuisine combination. When finding the highest rated cuisine, we search the cuisineFoodMap for the highest rated food-cuisine combination. If it exists, return the food; otherwise, search the foodMap for the highest rated food and cuisineMap for the corresponding cuisine, then update the food-cuisine combination in cuisineFoodMap.

